text: Vultures 2 (stylized in all caps) is the second collaborative album by Â¥$. It was released on August 3, 2024. On August 7, 2024, the website for Vultures was changed to sell a digital deluxe version of the album, with one bonus track: Take Off Your Dress. The next day, four more deluxe versions were added to the website, featuring the tracks "Believer", "Drunk", "Gun To My Head" and "Can U Be". All versions were sold for $5.
